1737: Referee Lee Mason is getting a bit card happy now, this time Andy Johnson having his name taken for a foul on Vincent Kompany chasing back.1735: Carlos Tevez is finally dragged from the field, Adam Johnson his replacement. A deserved ovation from the away supporters for their two-goal hero. Kolo Toure takes over the captaincy.
1734: Booking for Manchester City's Pablo Zabaleta for a foul on Diomansy Kamara.1731: Looks like Manchester City are contemplating replacing Carlos Tevez here, but the Argentine is having none of it. He can smell a hat-trick.
